les/Horammer.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Enchanter question... (sorry all)</span><hr size=1> I have an enchanter alt I got from a retired friend. I'm not sure of sites but I took him out to WC and played around with spell till I felt I knew what did what. Eq.castersrealm.com is good site for this.<br>Then I took him on some raids where I knew other chanters would be there and started playing with other spells Mez, charm, haste, C2.<br>Then I took him on some group where the mezzing is easy like the Hole.<br>Did small stuff like that till I was comfortable with playing him. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ujerodbreckmar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jerod Breckmar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Noble Squire</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/10/02 9:11:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15533.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Enchanter question... (sorry all)</span><hr size=1> I think castersrealm was the enchanter class site till it grew to encompass a lot more.  Even if it isnt the class site, it has a lot of info on enchanters.  Here is a link to a pretty complete guide (at least for my knowledge of the enchanter class):<br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/editorials/xymarra.asp">eq.castersrealm.com/editorials/xymarra.asp</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br><br>Jerod Breckmar<br>58 Paladin<br>Seventh Hammer <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uskyscreamer.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SkyScreamer</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Wandering Knight</span><br>  Posts: 127<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/10/02 9:14:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15533.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Enchanter question... (sorry all)</span><hr size=1> Chanters on raids: Haste, C3, tash, and mana drain mobs with mana.<br><br><br><br>Exp group: Mez(most stun first), haste, C3, tash, slow (if no shammy), and mana drain mobs with mana.<br><br>Very general, but play arpund with the generals and he will get it.<br> <p><BR><center><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6450>Sir Skyscreamer Apocalypse</a></center><center><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=13918>Master Khukri</a></center><center><a href=mailto:SkyScreamerLoS@aol.com>SkyScreamerLoS@aol.com</a></center><center><a href=http://www.legacyofsorrow.net/>Legacy of Sorrow</a></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uhunnfenu.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hunn Fenu</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Noble Squire</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/10/02 9:26:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15533.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Enchanter question... (sorry all)</span><hr size=1> Tell him to follow you around and give c2 and haste. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukassai.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kassai</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Noble Squire</span><br>  Posts: 41<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/10/02 10:09:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15533.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Enchanter question... (sorry all)</span><hr size=1> geez SkyScreamer..you make it sound so easy! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>&quot;Chanters on raids: Haste, C3, tash, and mana drain mobs with mana.&quot;<br>- it's all about perfect timing...cast tash too early and you are killed instantly..cast it too late, and you are slowing down chain of debuffs. mana drain is ineffective unless there are few enchanters around(you only need to drain mobs that can CH and can't be interrupted or mob that gates). enchanter is also responsible to dispelling mobs with buffs. anyway...<br><br>on typical raids...<br>- dispelling mob(since it must be done asap to avoid dispelling debuffs, you might gain aggro over mt if you aren't careful)<br>- tash, cripple, slow(high aggro spells, you need to learn right timing)<br>- mana drain(situational)<br>- aggro control(increase or decrease, relatively low aggro)<br>- rune(moderately high aggro)<br>- situational mez/crowd control(need to know which mobs can be mezzed and when to mez them), situational charm/crowd control(high aggro)<br>- buffs(kei, sos, vog,grm,cha buff)(repetitive..unless you have kei and epic stick)<br><br><br> <p><a HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=155102">Kassai</a><br><a HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=160626">Sfor</a><br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uvarutiasilvon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Varutia Silvon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Wandering Knight</span><br>  Posts: 117<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/11/02 7:35:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15533.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Enchanter question... (sorry all)</span><hr size=1> Chanter is not for weak hearted, they take so much beating and scary moments, it takes certain type of people to play them. Get him to read all the stuff he can on the eq.casterealm.com for enchanters that is a good start. Then find some lower level mobs to practice, tactices like mez, stun mez, chain stun, charm, slow, haste, mez timing, etc etc. Then practice, practice and practice, chanter is risky profession, but the rewards is great.<br><br>Need repeat this again, practice againist the mobs and get comfortable with playing chanter. Starting from zero to good chanter at 54 is not too easy, mobs hitting hard at that stage.<br> <p><center><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=177561>Varutia Silvonesit </a><BR>Level 56 Knight<BR>Terris Thule</center><BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bpaladinsofnorrath.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=ciladarholyblade>Ciladar Holyblade</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Blessed Protector</span><br>  Posts: 398<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/11/02 7:44:53 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15533.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Chanters</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://members.tripod.com/xornn/">members.tripod.com/xornn/</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> <br><br>excellent guide <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/urobsau.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Robsau</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Noble Squire</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/11/02 1:14:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15533.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Enchanter question... (sorry all)</span><hr size=1> Tell him that an Enchanter is useless and then offer to him that you could take the account for free  :P <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showPrevMessage?topicID=15533.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showNextMessage?topicID=15533.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15533.topic&index=8><img src=http://eq1.castersrealm.com/pon/images/reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.emailToFriend?topicID=15533.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.threadControl?topicID=15533.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=15533.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=15533.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right">